STATE EX REL. KERR
v.
COLLIER 2018-1329 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 28, 2018

O'CONNOR, C.J., and O'DONNELL, KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion for leave to amend denied.
